     data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
<script type="rocketlazyloadscript">
     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script></div>

<p>Photo courtesy: <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/guano/326497174" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">https://www.flickr.com/photos/guano/326497174</a>6</p>
<h3><span id="3_Electric_Secure_Fence">3) Electric Secure Fence</span></h3>
<div id="attachment_8303" style="width: 494px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-8303" class="size-full wp-image-8303" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20484%20363'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Electric Secure Fence" width="484" height="363" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.maritimemanual.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/secureshipfencingsystem.jpg 484w, https://www.maritimemanual.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/secureshipfencingsystem-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.maritimemanual.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/secureshipfencingsystem-150x113.jpg 150w, https://www.maritimemanual.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/secureshipfencingsystem-20x15.jpg 20w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 484px) 100vw, 484px" title="20 Anti-Piracy Weapons Deployed In Ships To Fight Pirates 17" data-lazy-src="https://www.maritimemanual.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/secureshipfencingsystem.jpg"><noscript><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-8303" class="size-full wp-image-8303" src="https://www.maritimemanual.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/secureshipfencingsystem.jpg" alt="Electric Secure Fence" width="484" height="363" srcset="https://www.maritimemanual.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/secureshipfencingsystem.jpg 484w, https://www.maritimemanual.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/secureshipfencingsystem-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.maritimemanual.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/secureshipfencingsystem-150x113.jpg 150w, https://www.maritimemanual.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/secureshipfencingsystem-20x15.jpg 20w" sizes="(max-width: 484px) 100vw, 484px" title="20 Anti-Piracy Weapons Deployed In Ships To Fight Pirates 17"></noscript><p id="caption-attachment-8303" class="wp-caption-text">Electric Secure Fence. Pics courtesy: http://www.delticgroup.com/secureshipfencingsystem.html</p><div class='code-block code-block-2' style='margin: 8px 0; clear: both;'>
<script type="rocketlazyloadscript" async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>
